title: BlackRock, Valkyrie Name Authorized Participants Including JPMorgan for Bitcoin ETF
description: BlackRock will use J.P. Morgan and Jane Street as their authorized participants. Valkyrie has also named Jane Street in addition to Cantor Fitzgerald.

title: PancakeSwap community passes proposal to reduce token supply by 300M
description:
In a landmark decision, decentralized exchange (DEX) PancakeSwap has successfully passed a proposal to reduce the total supply of its native token, CAKE, to a maximum cap of 450 million from  750 million.
